Bug Number 005
Monday, June 15, 1981 at 15:59:19

By: Jim Skowbo (JIM)
Re: fmt

Description:

Boldfacined titles are truncated. 
TBoldfaced two-digit page numbers in a title are skewed:  
e.g. for page 10, boldfaced output should be 1~1~10~0~0 (where ~ is backspace)
actual output is more like 10~10~10 (which doesn't come out right).
